，如有一期未經鐵育珊同意延期而未給付，視為全部到期。","JFULLPDF":"https://data.judicial.gov.tw/jdg/api/JDocFile/TNHM/111%2c%e4%b8%8a%e6%98%93%2c138%2c20221019%2c1/pdf"},"JID":"TNHM,111,上易,138,20221019,1","JYEAR":"111","JCASE":"上易","JNO":"138","JDATE":"20221019","JTITLE":"詐欺"}